'''Leonard Rosenman''' ([[7 September|September 7]], [[1924]] - [[4 March|March 4]], [[2008]]), was a prize-winning composer. Along with Paul Kont, he composed the soundtrack for [[The Lord of the Rings (1978 film)|''The Lord of the Rings '' film 1978]].
